    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> Caesari divi Nervae <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>divo Traiano Optumo <note>sic</note> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Germ</abbr><ex>anico</ex></expan> Dacico Parthico <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>pontif</abbr><ex>ici</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unicia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>potest</abbr><ex>ate</ex></expan> XXI <expan><abbr>imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>XIII co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> VI pater <note>sic</note> patriae optumo <note>sic</note> <lb n="6"/>maxumoque <note>sic</note> principi con<lb break="no" n="7"/>servatori generis humani <lb n="8"/>res publica Aratispitanorum <lb n="9"/>decrevit divo dedicavit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Erhalten ist der Mittelteil einer Statuenbasis. Mehrere Buchstaben sind nur handschriftlich überliefert. Datierung: nach der Konsekration Trajans im Sommer 118 n. Chr.</p>
            </div>
